<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1438,1231,2033]" pageId="2" pageNumber="17">
<emphasis box="[198,315,1622,1647]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="17">Structure:</emphasis>
mandible bidentate; basal area of labrum triangular with a central, elliptical depression; clypeus gently convex, not protuberant, with a weak, longitudinal, central depression; clypeoantennal distance slightly larger than diameter of antennal socket; inner eye margin slightly concave, eyes slightly converging bellow, except for upper end, converging above; ocelloccipital distance slightly larger than ocellar diameter; 
<emphasis box="[151,954,1776,1801]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="17">
interocellar and ocellocular distances about 
<number box="[689,726,1776,1801]" pageId="2" pageNumber="17" value="1.7">1.7</number>
ocellar diameters;
</emphasis>
vertex gently convex in facial view, not raised behing ocelli; malar area linear; scape surpassing lower margin of mid ocellus; surface of metapostnotum depressed in relation to lateral areas of propodeum; pygidial plate rounded apically, lateral margins diverging approximately in a 
<number box="[598,627,1892,1918]" pageId="2" pageNumber="17" value="60.0">60</number>
º angle.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1438,1231,2033]" pageId="2" pageNumber="17">
<emphasis box="[198,340,1931,1956]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="17">Body color:</emphasis>
body black except apical half of mandible, dark ferruginous (interrupted by blackish area); and distitarsi light ferruginous. 
<emphasis box="[518,988,1969,1994]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="17">Veins and pterostigma light ferruginous,</emphasis>
except Sc+R, brown; 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="17">wing membrane hyaline with yellowish hue especially basally and on marginal cell.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
